  <description><![CDATA[<p>A charming historic residence dating back to the 18<sup>th</sup> century, Castello Belvedere is situated in an idyllic panoramic location overlooking <a data-udi="umb://document/574a76e62f8b4388af2fd61b34c7ed1b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/574a76e62f8b4388af2fd61b34c7ed1b}" title="Desenzano">Desenzano</a> which lies 1.5km away. This characterful apartment complex lies on top of a hill, surrounded by 50,000m² of parkland. Castello Belvedere is a veritable haven 15 minutes’ walk outside of Desenzano’s historic centre. Enjoying wonderful lake views due to its position, the villa has been converted into apartments but many characterful details of the past remain, including the original chapel and gates. An excellent ‘agriturismo’ is next door producing excellent local dishes for those not wishing to stray far.</p>]]></description>
